 and having almost 1k aa and I still get owned tanking in RS the Nest and the lot is rediculous come on give u something useful not something we dont need or wont use.  We dont need Paci to work either whats the point if its only gonna work on lv 62 mobs.  We dont need a faster horse, and we sure as hell dont need a warrior telling us what we do and dont need.  Give us something we can use innately and full time.  Not something situational as always, that we cant utilize SU anyone?<br><br><br><br><br><br>Laedain	
