<DIV>While you are uping everyone else...give the warriors better weapons...and because they tank...how about class specific armor...with more hp and ac.</DIV>
<DIV>I find most warrior armor has Wisdom stats...why...?...Because it is also usable by clerics...or shamans...</DIV>
<DIV>Warriors are very gear dependant.&nbsp; And I find that most warriors can get the gear they need to fight in a zone AFTER they have advanced through the zone...</DIV>
<DIV>I played a warrior for my main until&nbsp;I got so frustrated that&nbsp;I changed classes.&nbsp; My warrior is now still 65 while my beastlord is 68.</DIV>
<DIV>I find beastlords, shamans, clerics and druids to be fun to play...</DIV>
<DIV>Warriors are very stressful to play...</DIV>
<DIV>When&nbsp;I &nbsp;group in the new zones,&nbsp; I find lots of lower level toons...except warriors...this is because warriors can't cut it..</DIV>
