<DIV>AND don't worry about takeing something away from warriors to compensate if you give them more class specific weapons and armor...to get them equal to their jobs...</DIV>
<DIV>Warriors are the only fighting class that can not heal itself...warriors can not cast invis on themselves...warriors don't have gate...</DIV>
<DIV>Warriors are very limited...</DIV>
